---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="sleep | human nature health"
  description="deep rest, recovery, and natural sleep rhythm."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">sleep</p>
      <h1>sleep is the foundation everything else builds on.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        energy, mood, recovery, hormones, and mental clarity all depend heavily on
        consistent, high-quality sleep.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what sleep actually does</h2>
        <p>
          during sleep the body repairs tissue, resets the brain, balances hormones,
          and restores energy systems. without it, everything becomes less stable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>what disrupts it</h2>
        <p>
          late-night light, screens, irregular schedules, stress, and overstimulation
          all make it harder for the body to enter deep rest.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>core principles</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>sleep at consistent times</p>
          <p>reduce light at night</p>
          <p>get sunlight early in the day</p>
          <p>avoid overstimulation before bed</p>
          <p>let the body wind down naturally</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section accent-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>simple sleep rhythm</h2>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>night</h3>
        <p>dim lights, reduce input, and allow the body to slow down.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>sleep</h3>
        <p>deep rest happens when the environment is calm and consistent.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h3>morning</h3>
        <p>get light early. it anchors your entire day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="quote-block">
        <p>better sleep fixes more than most people expect.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="y2k-panel feature-card">
        <div class="panel-heading-row">
          <p class="panel-kicker">checklist</p>
          <span class="panel-stamp">night</span>
        </div>
        <h2>simple sleep checklist</h2>
        <div class="content-list">
          <p>same sleep and wake time daily</p>
          <p>dim lights 60–90 min before bed</p>
          <p>no heavy scrolling late at night</p>
          <p>cool, dark sleeping environment</p>
          <p>morning sunlight within 30–60 min of waking</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="two-panel-grid">
        <a href="/start-here" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">previous</p>
          <h3>start here</h3>
          <p>begin with the core basics and simple pathway.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/sunlight" class="y2k-panel feature-card">
          <p class="panel-kicker">next</p>
          <h3>sunlight</h3>
          <p>continue into light, rhythm, and daily energy.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>